item.title: Review: Kohncertino
item.author: Timothy Kang,
item.description: Well, Imperial unquestionably has no shortage of orchestras, bands or music groups. However, there’s a new orchestra which has been growing in the past few months: Kohncertino. Led by first-year maths student Michael Kohn, Kohncertino held its debut concert on Saturday 16th March, at St Gabriel’s …
